SELECT 
  at.time + interval '10s' as time, 
  sum(at.threads) as "Threads",
  concat('Threads ', test_id)
FROM (
  SELECT time_bucket('10s', "timestamp") as time,
  locf(last(threads, timestamp)) as "threads",
  test_id
  FROM jmeter_metrics.thread_metric
  WHERE
  timestamp BETWEEN '2024-08-26T12:34:30.611Z' AND '2024-08-26T13:36:30.611Z' AND
  (-9999 in ('18686') OR test_id in ('18686')) AND
  ('%%all%%' in ('%%all%%') OR location IN ('%%all%%'))
  GROUP BY 1, container_id, test_id
  ORDER BY 1
) at
GROUP BY 1, test_id
ORDER BY 1
